library(rstan)
library(ggmcmc)

: n - 

set.seed(100)

N <- 100
true_p <- 0.65
N_test_questions <- 40
test_scores <- rbinom(N, N_test_questions, true_p)
data_1 <- list(N = length(test_scores), N_q = N_test_questions, X = test_scores) #    stan -   
model_1 <-
'
data {
  int<lower = 0> N;  //   ( 0)
  int<lower = 0> N_q; //   
  int<lower = 0> X[N]; //  -   N
}

parameters {
  real<lower = 0, upper = 1> p; //      
}

model {
  p ~ uniform(0.5, 1); //      
  for (i in 1:N){
    X[i] ~ binomial(N_q, p); //  
  }
}
'
fit_1 <- stan(model_code = model_1, #  
              data = data_1, #     
              chains = 3, #   (   ),     
              iter = 5000, #    
              warmup = 1000) #  ,
